flowchart TD
    A[Developer runs git commit] --> B[Git invokes .git/hooks/pre-commit]
    B --> C[driftlock hook-run]
    C --> D[Load configuration from .driftlock.toml]
    D --> E[Capture staged diff via git diff --cached]
    E --> F[Parse changed files with Tree-sitter to extract structural changes]
    F --> G[Map changed source files to documentation files using config]
    G --> H[For each doc file, read current content]
    H --> I[Prepare prompt variables: Diff, Doc, FileList]
    I --> J["Call LLM Provider.Check(diff, doc)"]
    J -->|Returns TRUE| K[Optional: Log SHA-256 hash to audit log / Solana]
    J -->|Returns FALSE| L["Call LLM Provider.Fix(diff, doc)"]
    L --> M["Write updated doc to working tree (overwrites file)"]
    M --> N["Print message: \"Commit blocked: docs updated for <file>. Review and stage.\""]
    N --> O[Exit 1]
    K --> P[Exit 0]